三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程將藉由案例研究以及分組報告深入瞭解英美刑法與刑事訴訟法之內涵。 


This course is designed to help students understand the basic system and concepts of criminal law and criminal procedure law in the Anglo-American legal system through case study and group presentation. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall DescriptionIn fall semester, we will focuse on the introduction of criminal law; criminal procedure will be introduced in spring semester. Following topics will be covered in this academic year:elements of crime, attempt, justification and excuse, criminal responsiblity, the 4th and 5th Amendments.


